lead_paragraph: Lionel Messi returned from a brief injury break to help Barcelona take the overnight lead in Spain, while Jamie Vardy found his scoring touch to boost Leicester's English Premier League title chase on Saturday.

headline.print_headline: Messi Scores on Return, Vardy Breaks Drought for Leicester
